title: Best of the Best with Clint Eastwood and Marco Rubio
itunes:title: Best of the Best with Clint Eastwood and Marco Rubio
description:
It's Labor Day weekend... Do you know what that's all about?
An interview with Macro Rubio from the RNC convention. A look at Cigar
Snob's Cigar Smoking Faux Pas, and Mr Jonathan interviews imaginary Clint
Eastwood! We're smoking the Padron 1964 Anniversary #4, and the extremely
limited Atabey.
